{"tid":1121520,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我女朋友話要同我分手 佢好撚仆街","createTime":"2019-04-23T11:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T09:44:12.000Z","uid":9581,"like":17,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"073311094f25c0cf654b237baa3a65b7329ebcca","tid":1121520,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"我同佢都係28碎 我本身無做野 佢就返緊份13k既工 <br />\n咁我無返工 佢養埋我都好應該 佢本身都會每個月比5-6k我用 <br />\n5-6k就唔係多 叫夠我平時食三餐 買下馬賭下錢咁(我贏錢都會請佢食飯)<br />\n自問對佢唔錯 起碼無搵其他女人 雞都只係叫過兩次<br />\n<br />\n我前晚allin左10k曼聯 豬撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我叫佢比住5k我買曼城追數啦 佢唔肯比仲要發脾氣話本身都唔夠錢用<br />\n自己搵得少都算 仲要鬧返我 我嬲嬲地打左佢一巴<br />\n佢就喊晒口咁話忍夠我 要分手 <br />\n<br />\n我贏錢個陣就係咁食我d野 輸錢問返佢借少少就唔得 <br />\n依d女只可以共富貴唔可以共患難 正仆街臭雞格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f435360ce74ee5aea80910a6c83980167e9c89","tid":1121520,"uid":125827,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"希望只係鳩UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6debac0e36cc67c7ae987c3dddfd12d5e656ac1c","tid":1121520,"uid":51485,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"曼聯咁垃圾都買 好難唔同你分手"},{"pid":"471258775e77690da4607b6fe73508bca293f85d","tid":1121520,"uid":115171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"5b4f140d63298156003cf9d1ccaa0ae7354aa41d","tid":1121520,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:17:58.000Z","msg":"波台d 人好垃圾"},{"pid":"ea4edb4c5f831871feccda0c47111856b7abf551","tid":1121520,"uid":79562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUCzfnQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h